Class ArraySet<E>

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Triangle2D
    public class ArraySet<E>
extends java.util.AbstractSet<E>
    An ArrayList implementation of Set. An ArraySet is good for small sets; it has less overhead than a HashSet or a TreeSet.
